{"tid":1130791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1圖測視力！ 網友實測：好準","createTime":"2019-04-29T09:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:04:08.000Z","uid":202698,"like":29,"dislike":251,"uniUserReply":172,"replies":[{"pid":"4c396cf6634811452cde5a8f3fc0639681e839d9","tid":1130791,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/fun/161510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2FNews%2Ffun%2F161510&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9aix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=9b5d128b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/fun/161510</a><br />\n<br />\n現代人因為3C產品普及，常會用眼過度影響視力健康，且根據統計，近幾年近視年齡層有下降的趨勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">網路上最近就瘋傳一張「視力測試圖」，要大家看看圖中分別是哪4個數字，藉此就可以測出眼睛是否有近視、散光</span>，不少網友實測後，看到解答都驚呼很玄<span style=\"color: red;\">「超準的」</span>，但也有人哭笑不得地說<span style=\"color: red;\">「我怎每次看都不同」</span>，該話題意外掀起討論。<br />\n<br />\n網友在臉書社團《爆廢公社公開版》曬出一張圖，並在貼文寫道，「看看數字是什麼？稍後給答案！」只見圖中為黑色背景，上頭佈滿密密麻麻的白色小圓點，正中間隱約浮現了4個數字，原PO還特別強調這是「眼科醫生視力權威檢測」的圖片，而他隨後也公佈4組不同答案及其涵義，分別是「3246，近視加散光」、「3240，散光不近視」、「1246，光近視不散光」、「1240，眼睛相當健康」<br />\n<br />\n▼網友曬出視力測試圖。（圖／翻攝自爆廢公社公開版）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/04/26/1556292999_73514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F1556292999_73514.jpg&h=5f9cc7c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6f470173cd649ff8d902dd986a4d5d26daf8546","tid":1130791,"uid":133529,"like":378,"dislike":23,"score":355,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"我帶眼鏡1246。唔帶乜鳩都睇唔到"},{"pid":"015d34c7370b42ad412179dcd7dc280d7af6bc6d","tid":1130791,"uid":48579,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:34:14.000Z","msg":"拉遠啲先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df00d9919649eb71cc84834eb64e0f4d33af3f3","tid":1130791,"uid":203783,"like":718,"dislike":15,"score":703,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-29